Package: miRHeat
Type: Package
Title: Tools for miRNA–UTR Interaction Filtering and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person(
        given = "Maria",
        family = "Nicoletti",
        email = "maria.nicoeltti@unesp.br",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
      )
    )
Description: Tools to process, filter and visualize miRNA–UTR interaction predictions.
    Includes functions to parse RNAhybrid or IntaRNA output files, filter by
    interaction energy and seed pairing, and convert results into tidy data frames
    and heatmaps for comparative visualization.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
